==English==

===Noun===
'''Buddha''' (''plural:'' [[Buddhas]])

# Indian spiritual and philosophical teacher and founder of ''[[Buddhism]].''
# an enlightened human being.
# a statue or image of the Buddha.

===Alternative spellings===
*[[buddha]] (senses 2 and 3 only)

===Derived terms===
*[[Buddhahood]]
*[[Buddhism]]
*[[Buddhist]]

